#: server/activities/reversecount/ReversecountEditor.qml:27
msgctxt "ReversecountEditor|"
msgid ""
"\"Maximum number\" is the maximum number which can be entered on each side "
"of the domino."
msgstr ""
"\"Maximum getal\" is het maximum getal dat ingevoerd kan worden aan elke "
"kant van de domino."

#: server/activities/reversecount/ReversecountEditor.qml:29
msgctxt "ReversecountEditor|"
msgid ""
"The maximum interval is the smaller of 15 and 2 × \"Domino maximum number\"."
msgstr ""
"Het maximum interval is het kleinste van 15 en 2 × \"Maximum getal van domino"
"\"."

#: server/activities/reversecount/ReversecountEditor.qml:31
msgctxt "ReversecountEditor|"
msgid ""
"\"Intervals\" must contain integer numbers between 1 and the maximum "
"interval. These numbers will be selected randomly for each question. You can "
"enter several times the same number to increase the probability that it will "
"be selected."
msgstr ""
"\"Intervallen\" moet gehele getallen tussen 1 en het maximum interval "
"bevatten. Deze getallen zullen willekeurig gesel worden voor elke vraag. U "
"kunt verschillende keren hetzelfde getal invoeren om de waarschijnlijkheid "
"dat het zal worden geselecteerd te verhogen."

